        "subject": "LU-2215 dne: misc fixes for osp on OST.",
        "message": "LU-2215 dne: misc fixes for osp on OST.\n\n1. return 0 instead of 1 if quota param is not being\nchanged.\n\n2. Only stop MDT0--osp--MDT0 in lustre_disconnect_osp,\nand other OSPs on MDT will be stoped in mdt stack\ncleanup.\n\n3. Change name of is_osp_on_ost to is_osp_for_mdt0, and\nmake sure it only return true if the osp is for MDT0-osp-MDT0.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I197666a5356b8f4701a9f3c7ac2e233c9e35ce01\n"
